Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 7
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Tsukune Aono’s new school is filled with vampires and werewolves. How is a human teenager to survive?
Title: ROSARIO   VAMPIRE, VOL. 8
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: Jiraiya, ninja and mentor to Naruto, put everything he learned about the Akatsuki organization in code. Can Naruto decipher it in time?
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 45
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: This series is about a family that is possessed by the animals of the Chinese zodiac. Secrets from the past are revealed and Akito, head of the clan, finds her control slipping.
Title: FRUITS BASKET, VOL. 23
Author: Natsuki Takaya

Description: The protagonist: 15-year-old Allen Walker. The setting: 19th century England. His mission: to find Innocence, a substance used to create weapons to destroy the akuma demons.
Title: D. GRAY-MAN, VOL. 14
Author: Katsura Hoshino

Description: Daisuke Niwa is an ordinary middle school student under a cruse that turns him into a phantom. The only way to cure him is to get Risa, the girl he adores, to fall for him.
Title: D. N. ANGEL, VOL. 12
Author: Yukiru Sugisaki

Description: Asuka Masamune, one his school’s jocks, is hiding a secret. He really likes cooking, manga for girls and sewing. Will him falling for Ryo Miyakozuka, the daughter of a martial artist, help him?
Title: OTOMEN 3
Author: Aya Kanno

Description: Two brothers harmed in a ritual that was half magic/half science seek the legendary Philosopher’s Stone to make things right. This installment reveals their father’s origin.
Title: FULLMETAL ALCHEMIST, VOL. 19
Author: Hiromu Arakawa

Description: Misao Harada can see the magic hidden in the world, but it turns out to be a a power that demons wants to exploit. Will her childhood friend, Kyo, who is the head of a demon clan, help or hurt her?
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 1
Author: Kanoko Sakurakoji

Description: The dilapidated house Kiyo’s grandmother left her comes complete with two vampires: Kuroboshi and his servant, Alshu. Will it be love at first bite?
Title: BLOODY KISS, VOL. 1
Author: Kazuko Furumiya
